Titolo: American Pool

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: American Pool (known as Billiard King in Japan) is a Sports simulation video game released for the PlayStation.The game offers three game modes. Training mode lets the players learn the controls and techniques of the game while playing in trickshot-style levels. pocket Game lets players play against either the computer or a friend in five different pool games; 9-Ball, 8-Ball, Basic, Rotation and 14-1 Rack. Pool Contest is a tournament mode which they can create their own player and earn special skills.